it was so ethnocentric,

00:28:13.260 --> 00:28:15.204
China is very open
to foreign managers.

00:28:15.204 --> 00:28:16.620
So if you send
someone there, they

00:28:16.620 --> 00:28:20.670
get the chance to manage
Chinese people, people

00:28:20.670 --> 00:28:21.970
from other countries.

00:28:21.970 --> 00:28:24.860
So we now have a saying, to
paraphrase Frank Sinatra's

00:28:24.860 --> 00:28:28.260
song, Shanghai, Shanghai,
if you can manage there,

00:28:28.260 --> 00:28:31.020
you can manage anywhere.

